articles.title: Clustering-predicted structures at the scale of the known protein universe - Nature.com
articles.description: The novel Foldseek clustering algorithm defines 2.30 million clusters of AlphaFold structures, identifying remote structural similarity of human immune-related proteins in prokaryotic species.
